-- KKR Says Ex-Willis Chief Plumeri Joins Buyout Firm as Adviser
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2013-08-19T20:22:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-19/kkr-says-ex-willis-chief-plumeri-joins-buyout-firm-as-adviser.html
KKR & Co., the private-equity firm
run by Henry Kravis and  George Roberts , said Joseph Plumeri is
joining as a senior adviser and becoming a director at payments
company First Data.  Plumeri was previously the chief executive officer of
 Willis Group Holdings Plc (WSH) , a former KKR investment, according to
a statement today from the New York-based buyout firm.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
 nbuhayar@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  